<h1>Help</h1>
<p>To sign up for an account on YATC, all you need to do is supply a name for yourself and a valid e-mail address. Once you're signed in...</p>
<ul><li>Click on <%= link_to "Home", root_path %> to write a new micropost. Here, you can also view all the microposts of those you
are following, and yours too.</li>
<li>Head over to <% if signed_in? %><%= link_to "Users", users_path %><% else %>Users<% end %> to see who else is signed up on YATC. Click on their
names or profile pictures to view their profiles. To follow another user, head over to his or her profile page and click on the Follow button below
his or her profile picture. To unfollow someone, simply click on the Unfollow button, also on the user's profile page.</li>
<li>To view your own profile, check out the <% if signed_in? %><%= link_to "Profile", current_user %><% else %>Profile<% end %> page. Below your
profile picture is a status feed that contains only your microposts. If you want see all the people whom you are following, click on the
following link on the right-hand side of your profile page. To list those who are following you, click on the appropriately named followers link.</li>
<li>You can change your name, e-mail address, password, and avatar via the <% if signed_in? %><%= link_to "Settings", edit_user_path(current_user) %>
<% else %>Settings<% end %> page. Avatars are hosted on <a href="http://www.gravatar.com" target="_blank">Gravatar</a>, so to upload your own and use
it on YATC, or use an avatar that is already on Gravatar, you have to sign up for an account with them first.</li></ul>
